# Privacy Policy – Penalgo

Last updated: 29.01.2026

## 1. General Information
Penalgo is an insulin calculation app. The app does not collect, store, or share any personal data.

## 2. Data Collection
Penalgo does **not** collect:
- Personal information
- Health data on servers
- Location data
- Analytics or tracking data

All calculations are performed **locally on the device**.

## 3. Third-Party Services
Penalgo does not use third-party analytics, advertising, or tracking services.

## 4. Data Storage
All entered values remain on the user’s device. No cloud storage is used.

## 5. User Rights
Since no personal data is collected, no data deletion or export is required.

## 6. Contact
If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, contact:

Email: prnalgo14nov@gmail.com
